BANDAGE: First aid on a wounded target

Syntax: bandage <target>
        treat <target>

DESCRIPTION:
  Bandage or treat wounds on a living target in the same room. Requires the
  First Aid skill and bandages, a first aid kit, or a medkit in inventory.

NOTES:
  A successful roll restores a small amount of SDC or HP.
  treat and bandage are the same command.
  Body Fixers and other medical OCCs may have better healing options.

SEE ALSO: treat, skills, rest
